Valerio Galli</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/vitaliy-kovalchuk/" rel="tag">Vitaliy Kovalchuk</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/yvonne-manfreda/" rel="tag">Yvonne Manfreda</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/zanetto/" rel="tag">Zanetto</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Alessandra Masini, Alessio Pizzech, Carlotta Vichi, Cavalleria rusticana, Cristina Martufi, Mamuka Lomidze, Maria Salvini, Opera lirica, Pietro Mascagni, recensioni, Teatro Goldoni di Livorno, Valerio Galli, Vitaliy Kovalchuk, Yvonne Manfreda, Zanetto"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/9ba640a7ac7b6985c46cf498c1470596" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Nicola-Lischi-116x150.jpg" width="77" height="100" alt="Nicola Lischi" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Nicola Lischi"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/nicola-lischi/">View all articles by Nicola Lischi</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/12/new-york-metropolitan-opera-la-donna-del-lago/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> New York, Metropolitan Opera: &#8220;La donna del lago&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/12/susanna-di-handel-allauditorio-nacional-di-madrid/" rel="next">“Susanna” di Händel all’Auditorio Nacional di Madrid <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2015/12/il-dittico-zanettocavalleria-rusticana-a-livorno/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sarà pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name="author" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="245" aria-required='true' required='required' /></p><p class="comment-form-email"><label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="email" name="email" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="100" aria-describedby="email-notes" aria-required='true' required='required' /></p><p class="comment-form-url"><label for="url">Sito web</label> <input id="url" name="url" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="200" /></p><p class="form-submit"><input name="submit" type="submit" id="submit" class="submit" value="Commento all&#039;articolo" /> <input type='hidden' name='comment_post_ID' value='83352' id='comment_post_ID' /> <input type='hidden' name='comment_par